        // server (/api/state) then falls back to local storage.
        //
        // Hydrate() merges loaded data into State, handling two legacy formats (habits as
        // plain strings vs. objects) and filtering out corrupted items.
        //
        // Save() is debounced 300ms to avoid hammering the server during rapid typing.
```

