**Location to insert**: Before `let saveTimer;` (current file line 807)
```
        // ─── DEBOUNCED SAVE ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
        // Every keystroke in a text input would trigger a network request if we saved
        // immediately. Instead we reset a 300ms timer on each call — only when typing
        // pauses for 300ms does the actual POST /api/state fire.
```

